fields.name: Suffolk Free Range Chicken
fields.description: Beautiful free range chicken from the heart of suffolk. Ranging in sizes of: 1.4kg, 1.8kg, 2.2kg. Always raised in smaller flock sizes by farmers who are passionate about their animals welfare and life before coming to your table.

fields.name: Chicken Breast - Pack of 5
fields.description: Beautiful free range chicken breasts from the heart of suffolk. Always raised in smaller flock sizes by farmers who are passionate about their animals welfare and life before coming to your table.

fields.name: Rolled Beef Rib
fields.description: Rolled Beef Rib . Expertly trimmed and rolled by our expert butchers. Weight: 2KG. A large joint of meat with a deliciously meaty flavour and strong marbling. The bone is removed and the joint is rolled and tied for easy carving.

fields.name: Rolled Beef Sirloin
fields.description: Rolled Beef Sirloin . Expertly trimmed and rolled by our expert butchers. Weight: 1KG. A large joint of meat with a deliciously meaty flavour and strong marbling. The bone is removed and the joint is rolled and tied for easy carving.

fields.name: Whole Beef Fillet
fields.description: Whole Beef Fillet . Expertly trimmed and rolled by our expert butchers. Weight: 1KG. A large joint of meat with a deliciously meaty flavour and strong marbling. The bone is removed and the joint is rolled and tied for easy carving.

fields.name: Beef Burgers - Pack of Four
fields.description: Beef Burgers expertly hand crafted and seasoned to perfection by our by butchers. Grill them on the bbq for your ultimate summer family get together, or on a cold winters night for that delicious comfort food need.

fields.name: T-Bone Steak
fields.description: T-Bone steak. Expertly trimmed and cut by our expert butchers. Weight: 450g-500g per steak. A prime sharing steak, cut through and left on the bone, both sirloin and fillet with maximum flavour. Dry-aged for a minimum of 21 days..

fields.name: Sirloin Steak - Pack of two
fields.description: Sirloin Steak . Expertly trimmed and cut by our expert butchers. Weight: 170g pack of two. A prime sharing steak, cut through and left on the bone, both sirloin and fillet with maximum flavour. Dry-aged for a minimum of 21 days..

fields.name: Fillet Steaks - Pack of two
fields.description: Beef Fillet Steaks . Expertly trimmed and cut by our expert butchers. Weight: 170g pack of two. A prime sharing steak, cut through and left on the bone, both sirloin and fillet with maximum flavour. Dry-aged for a minimum of 21 days..

fields.name: Ribeye Steaks - Pack of two
fields.description: Ribeye Steaks. Expertly trimmed and cut by our expert butchers. Weight: 170g pack of two. A prime sharing steak, cut through and left on the bone, both sirloin and fillet with maximum flavour. Dry-aged for a minimum of 21 days..

fields.name: Beef Mince - 2kg
fields.description: Beef Mince. Expertly trimmed and cut and ground by our expert butchers. Weight: 2KG. Versatile with a great ratio of fat to meat providing a deep flavoursome taste upon cooking. Combining both sirloin fillet and rump for maximum flavour. Dry-aged for a minimum of 21 days..

fields.name: Rump Steaks - Pack of two
fields.description: Rump Steaks. Expertly trimmed and cut by our expert butchers. Weight: 170g pack of two. A prime sharing steak, cut through and left on the bone. Dry-aged for a minimum of 21 days..

fields.name: Pork Loin Boned and Rolled
fields.description: Pork Loin Boned and Rolled. Expertly trimmed, boned and rolled by our expert butchers. Weight: 3KG. Perfect for roasting. We cut a piece of pork loin and debone it whilst leaving the rind on to ensure crackling successes.

fields.name: Pork Shoulder
fields.description: Pork Shoulder Boned and Rolled. Expertly trimmed, boned and rolled by our expert butchers. Weight: 3KG. Perfect for roasting. We carefully prepare and debone the joint whilst leaving the rind on to ensure crackling successes.

fields.name: Pork Rib - French Trimmed
fields.description: Pork Loin Boned and Rolled. Expertly trimmed and prepared by our expert butchers. 5 Bone Rack. Gloucester Old Spot French Trimmed Rack of Pork, ideal for the perfect family roast. A rack of pork from the rib area with a delicious eye of meat and a good layer of fat for delicious crackling.

fields.name: Pork Chops - Pack of four
fields.description: Pork Chops - Pack of four. Each pork chop is expertly trimmed and prepared by our expert butchers. Weight: 150g Per Chop. A British favourite of delicious pork cut into chops by our butchers, Pork Chops are an amazing cut. Perfect for quick mid-week meals or marinating as a barbecue dish. These have a deep impressive flavour because of the outdoor reared pork we use.

fields.name: Old English Sausages - Pack of six
fields.description: Old English Sausages. Each sausage is lovingly handcrafted by our team of expert butchers and chefs. Hand made with our outdoor reared Gloucester Old Spot pork and Old English seasoning, these sausages are freshly made on site by our own butchers.

fields.name: Maple Cured Bacon
fields.description: Maple Syrup Cured Bacon. Sliced Maple Back Bacon produced using our Gloucester Old Spot Pork, this Maple Syrup Cured Back Bacon is soaked for two weeks in finest canadian maple syrup, giving it that tasty maple flavour.

fields.name: Steaky Back Bacon
fields.description: Steaky Back Bacon. Our bacon is all produced from our own pork and is traditionally dry cured. Amazing quality product with a deep full flavour.

fields.name: Back Bacon
fields.description: Sliced Back Bacon. Our bacon is all produced from our own pork and is traditionally dry cured. Amazing quality product with a deep full flavour.

fields.name: Lamb Rack
fields.description: Lamb Rack with 4 bones. Simple, impressive and delicious.  Great for roasting, the rack is the lambs most premium cut – lean, tender and packed with flavour.

fields.name: Diced Lamb
fields.description: Diced Lamb. Expertly prepared by our team of butchers. Weight: 1KG. Grass-fed British diced lamb. Perfect for stews and pies.

fields.name: Lamb Mince
fields.description: Minced Lamb. Expertly prepared by our team of butchers. Weight: 1KG. Grass-fed British diced lamb. Perfect for stews and pies.

fields.name: Lamb Rumps - Pack of two
fields.description: Lamb Rumps. Expertly prepared by our team of butchers. Weight: 170-180g Pack of two. Grass-fed British diced lamb. Perfect for stews and pies.

fields.name: Cod Side
fields.description: Whole cod side. The classic go-to for fish and chips, cod is a big coldwater fish, prized for their dense, yet flaky flesh.

fields.name: Rainbow Trout
fields.description: Rainbow Trout. Perfect for roasting whole, stuffing or turning into a papiot

fields.name: Dover Sole

fields.name: Haddock Portions

fields.name: Salmon Portions
fields.description: Individual Salmon Portions. Weight: 160-180G. Perfect for pan frying with some lemon butter. Baking, poaching or grilling.

fields.name: Whole Crab

fields.name: Handpicked Crab Meat
